race.comment: There was only a length between VERONA ROSE (2) and OH DIAMOND LIL (1) when they met at Newcastle in the G3 Tibbie Stakes. VERONA ROSE finished second on that occasion and started longer in the market but does meet her 2kg better at the weights and her form since has been better. Eighth to Autumn Glow in the Epsom was solid, fourth to Idle Flyer in a very fast G3 Angst Stakes last time reads well. OH DIAMOND LIL has been poor in two since albeit not far away in the G2 Invitation last time. She lands on speed and can bounce back. KEEP YOUR COOL (4) continues to race well, trying hard behind Ndola last time. Gets Zahra aboard now and should take beating again. MOONLIGHT CIRCUS (9) is going well and is proven at a mile. Her run for third at Caulfield last time is solid form. SNEAKY SUNRISE (6) can improve third up out to 1600m and wouldn't surprise at all.
